       <!-- SERVICE 1.1 - 100 GREAT SUPPLY CHAIN PARTNERS -->
       <div class="first_item slide_item">
        <img alt="100 Great Supply Chain Partners" complete="complete" src="/Images/100GreatSCPartners2017.jpg" style="width: 438px; height: 254px;"/>
        <h3>
         Top 100 Great Supply Chain Partners
        </h3>
        <p>
         St. Onge Company is honored to be elected, for the eighth time in the last ten years and for the last five years in a row, to the Top 100 Great Supply Chain Partners list. We were nominated by our clients among thousands of other respected organizations, and are pleased to be recognized as one of the best.
        </p>
        <a href="http://www.supplychainbrain.com/content/fileadmin/images/PDFS/2015_PARTNERS_CHART.pdf" shape="rect" target="_blank">
         <img alt="Click to read more" complete="complete" src="/Images/ui/hm-button-learnmore.gif" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" title="Learn more about services for supply chain strategy"/>
        </a>
       </div>
       <!-- SERVICE 1.5 - BECKERS-->
       <div class="slide_item">
        <img alt="Becker's Hospital Review" complete="complete" height="254" src="/Images/beckers.jpg" title="Becker's Hospital Review" width="438"/>
        <h3>
         Becker's Hospital Review Publication
        </h3>
        <p>
         St. Onge Company's Tom Redding outlines a Supply Chain Assessment for your healthcare system in an article published by
         <em>
          Becker's Hospital Review
         </em>
         . Click Learn More to read the full article on the
         <em>
          Becker's Hospital Review
         </em>
         website!
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.beckershospitalreview.com/supply-chain/don-t-become-a-healthcare-statistic.html" shape="rect" target="_blank">
         <img alt="Read Tom Redding's article on the Becker's Hospital Review website" complete="complete" src="/Images/ui/hm-button-learnmore.gif" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" title="Read Tom Redding's article on the Becker's Hospital Review website"/>
        </a>
       </div>
       <!-- SERVICE 1 - INTRO SOC-->
       <div class="slide_item">
        <img alt="" complete="complete" src="/Images/hm-service-welcome3.jpg"/>
        <h3>
         Supply Chain Consulting Experience
        </h3>
        <p>
         For over 30 years St. Onge has been a leader in the supply chain management industry. Our integrated service offerings span the planning, engineering, specification, implementation management and systems integration within logistics networks and advanced material handling manufacturing.
        </p>
       </div>
       <!-- SERVICE 2 - SUPPLY CHAIN STRATEGY -->
       <div class="slide_item">
        <img alt="Supply Chain Strategy" complete="complete" src="/Images/supply chain strategy 1.jpg" style="width: 438px; height: 254px;"/>
        <h3>
         Supply Chain Strategy and Logistics
        </h3>
        <p>
         St. Onge has performed over 400 strategic network studies for more than 200 different clients. These clients span a wide range of industries across the globe including food &amp; beverage, building materials, CPG, military/government, hospital and life science, industrial and retail/wholesale.
        </p>
        <a href="/what_we_do/supply_chain_engineering.aspx" shape="rect">
         <img alt="Learn more about services for supply chain strategy" complete="complete" src="/Images/ui/hm-button-learnmore.gif" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" title="Learn more about services for supply chain strategy"/>
        </a>
       </div>
       <!-- SERVICE 3 - DISTRIBUTION DESIGN -->
       <div class="slide_item">
        <img alt="Distribution Design" complete="complete" src="/Images/hm-service-distribution.jpg" style="width: 438px; height: 254px;"/>
        <h3>
         Warehousing and Distribution Design
        </h3>
        <p>
         We have completed warehousing and distribution design engagements all over the world. In total, our warehousing solutions have served over 750 clients and completed over 4,000 successful assignments.
        </p>
        <a href="/what_we_do/warehousing_distribution_design.aspx" shape="rect">
         <img alt="Learn more about servics for distribution design" complete="complete" src="/Images/ui/hm-button-learnmore.gif" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" title="Learn more about servics for distribution design"/>
        </a>
       </div>
       <!-- SERVICE 4 - MFG DESIGN -->
       <div class="slide_item">
        <img alt="Manufacturing Design" complete="complete" src="/Images/york I mfg.jpg" style="width: 438px; height: 254px;"/>
        <h3>
         Manufacturing Design
        </h3>
        <p>
         We provide a complete range of business consulting, engineering and logistics services to support developing global manufacturing strategies. These range from strategic sourcing initiatives, new manufacturing facility design or expansion to operations improvement and six sigma processes.
        </p>
        <a href="/what_we_do/manufacturing_design.aspx" shape="rect">
         <img alt="Learn more about services for manufacturing design" complete="complete" src="/Images/ui/hm-button-learnmore.gif" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" title="Learn more about services for manufacturing design"/>
        </a>
       </div>
       <!-- SERVICE 5 - HOSPITAL DESIGN -->
       <div class="slide_item">
        <img alt="Hospital Design" complete="complete" height="254" src="/Images/CHHS_3Dimage.jpg" title="Hospital Design" width="438"/>
        <h3>
         Hospital Design
        </h3>
        <p>
         At St. Onge we are continually enhancing our life science offerings, specifically the challenging logistics and real-time issues associated with hospital operations. We offer planning, design and operational solutions for clients ranging from manufacturers and wholesalers to retailers of medical devices, prescription Rx and over the counter products.
        </p>
        <a href="/what_we_do/hospital_medcenter.aspx" shape="rect">
         <img alt="Learn more about services for hospital design" complete="complete" src="/Images/ui/hm-button-learnmore.gif" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" title="Learn more about services for hospital design"/>
        </a>
       </div>
       <!-- SERVICE 6 - MILITARY/GOV-->
       <div class="slide_item">
        <img alt="Military and Government" complete="complete" height="254" src="/Images/ships.jpg" title="Military and Government" width="438"/>
        <h3>
         Military / Government
        </h3>
        <p>
         We have a long standing and successful relationship with the United States Armed Forces, the U.S. Government and their preferred sub contractors. Our supply chain strategy, operations and facility design and 3PL procurement service offerings have proven themselves valuable across multiple government engagements.
        </p>
        <a href="/what_we_do/military_government.aspx" shape="rect">
         <img alt="Learn more about services for military and government" complete="complete" src="/Images/ui/hm-button-learnmore.gif" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" title="Learn more about services for military and government"/>
        </a>
       </div>
       <!-- SERVICE 7 - SYSTEMS & TECH-->
       <div class="slide_item">
        <img alt="Systems and Technologies" complete="complete" height="254" src="/Images/hm-service-systems.jpg" title="Systems and Technologies" width="438"/>
        <h3>
         Systems &amp; Technologies
        </h3>
        <p>
         Our systems specialists work to ensure that automated identification, information management and control systems technologies are aligned to meet your operational expectations. Our consulting services include requirements definition, justification, evaluation and selection implementation of supply chain planning and execution systems.
        </p>
        <a href="/what_we_do/systems_technologies.aspx" shape="rect">
         <img alt="Learn more about services for systems and technologies" complete="complete" src="/Images/ui/hm-button-learnmore.gif" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: solid;" title="Learn more about services for systems and technologies"/>
        </a>
       </div>

 <h3>3PL Selection and Advisory</h3>
 <p>St. Onge provides experienced insight into third-party logistics (3PL) capabilities in a wide variety of business types and supply chain segments. We offer approaches that assist you in making the decision to outsource your logistics services, and ensure operations flexibility, cost savings and improved service levels. </p>

      <div id="homeContentWrapper">
       <div id="aboutText">
        <h2>
         Supply Chain Engineering
        </h2>
        St. Onge is a world-recognized supply chain strategy and logistics consulting firm. Our discovery-driven approach brings together the elements of supply chain logistics, engineering and operations to ensure that the supply chain challenges you face will be met with unique answers that fit your needs. From guiding strategy development to coordinating global logistics network optimization, each of our clients receives a custom solution.
        <p>
         By partnering with St. Onge you can reduce the cost of your supply chain, implement service improvements to your distribution network, reduce inventory and increase your business process efficiencies.
         <a href="/contact/lets_talk.aspx">
          Contact us
         </a>
         today and begin to manage your supply chain more effectively.
        </p>
        <a href="/about_us/values.aspx">
         <img alt="Read more about St. Onge" src="/Images/ui/hm-button-readmore.gif" title="Read more about St.Onge"/>
        </a>
        <!-- / end about text -->
